"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Hardware Requirements\\n\\n## Minimum Specs\\n\\nThe minimum recommended specs for running a node is the following:\\n\\n- 16-core, x86_64 architecture processor\\n- 64 GiB RAM\\n- 500 GiB of locally attached SSD storage\\n\\nFor example, an AWS instance like the `r6id.4xlarge`, or equivalent.\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/nodes/running-node/hardware-requirement#hardware-requirements\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/running-node/hardware-requirement.mdx#hardware-requirements\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\n\",\"title\":\"Hardware Requirements\",\"titles\":[]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/running-node/hardware-requirement#minimum-specs\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>The minimum recommended specs for running a node is the following:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>16-core, x86_64 architecture processor</li>\\n<li>64 GiB RAM</li>\\n<li>500 GiB of locally attached SSD storage</li>\\n</ul>\\n<p>For example, an AWS instance like the <code>r6id.4xlarge</code>, or equivalent.</p>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/running-node/hardware-requirement.mdx#minimum-specs\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nThe minimum recommended specs for running a node is the following:\\n\\n16-core, x86_64 architecture processor\\n64 GiB RAM\\n500 GiB of locally attached SSD storage\\n\\nFor example, an AWS instance like the r6id.4xlarge, or equivalent.\",\"title\":\"Minimum Specs\",\"titles\":[\"Hardware Requirements\"]}]}}"
